🧑‍💻 1. User Management
POST    /api/auth/register/
POST    /api/auth/login/
POST    /api/auth/logout/
POST    /api/auth/password-reset/
POST    /api/auth/verify-email/
POST    /api/auth/social-link/  # Link Facebook/Google

GET     /api/user/profile/
PUT     /api/user/profile/update/

🎵 2. Music Track Vote (Live Queue Voting System)
POST    /api/events/create/
GET     /api/events/public/
GET     /api/events/private/
POST    /api/events/{event_id}/join/
POST    /api/events/{event_id}/tracks/suggest/
POST    /api/events/{event_id}/tracks/{track_id}/vote/
GET     /api/events/{event_id}/tracks/

🕹️ 3. Music Control Delegation
POST    /api/control/delegate/
GET     /api/control/delegates/
POST    /api/control/play/
POST    /api/control/pause/
POST    /api/control/skip/

📃 4. Music Playlist Editor (Collaborative Playlists)
POST    /api/playlists/create/
GET     /api/playlists/public/
GET     /api/playlists/private/
POST    /api/playlists/{playlist_id}/invite/
POST    /api/playlists/{playlist_id}/tracks/add/
DELETE  /api/playlists/{playlist_id}/tracks/{track_id}/remove/
POST    /api/playlists/{playlist_id}/tracks/reorder/
GET     /api/playlists/{playlist_id}/tracks/

📦 6. Optional (but likely needed)
GET     /api/licenses/
POST    /api/licenses/assign/

